I loved this salad! It was easy to make (could even prepare ahead of time) and looked great for guests or for a casual dinner. I have had many requests from my table for the recipe. I would agree the key is the lemon zest. Also for variation think of this as an antipasta platter you could add other ingrediants such as marinated mushrooms, roasted peppers, fresh small mozzerella balls etc. Might be a different change of pace!

